  "description": "A large, roomy, modern Side-by-side refrigerator belongs to the high price segment and is an advanced model with many functions and technologies that make the device more efficient. The inverter linear compressor reduces temperature fluctuations, maintains stable operation of the device and is reliable and durable. The Multi Air Flow cooling system and DoorCooling+ technology ensure even distribution of cool air throughout the chamber, thus helping to keep food fresh longer. The Total No Frost system prevents the formation of ice and frost and eliminates the need for the user to manually defrost the refrigerator and freezer compartments. The feature of the model is an external dispenser located on the door, which supplies chilled water. Water comes from a special tank, which is filled manually. Its volume is 4 liters. Moreover, the dispenser cleans itself using ultraviolet light. And the LG GS-LV91MBAC is a smart device that can connect to Wi-Fi and synchronize with a mobile application. In it you can adjust the refrigerator settings, receive error notifications and useful tips. In addition, the device understands voice commands. The total useful volume is an impressive 635 liters, so there is definitely enough space for groceries and utensils with ready-made food. The refrigerator features four durable tempered glass shelves, a separate bottle rack, side shelves, egg trays and a Moist Balance Crisper that maintains optimal humidity levels for storing vegetables, fruits and herbs. The freezer offers several pull-out compartments and is capable of freezing 12 kg of food per day. There is also an internal backlight, quick freezing and cooling functions, a convenient touch control panel with a display, the ability to lock the controls (child protection) and an indicator indicating that the door is not closed.",
